edu.rit.aes

Class AES256

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.rit.crst.Computation
      • edu.rit.crst.Function
        • edu.rit.aes.AESBase
          • edu.rit.aes.AES256

  • public class AES256
extends AESBase
    Class AES256 implements the AES block cipher with a 256-bit key. The AES256 cryptographic function's input A is the plaintext (128 bits); input B is the key (256 bits); output C is the ciphertext (128 bits).
